<p>This project was done as a display project by the <a href="https://erc-bpgc.github.io/projects.html"><strong>Electronics and Robotics Club</strong></a>, for <strong>Quark</strong>, the technical fest of BITS Goa. The project was displayed on Day 3 of Quark 2019 <em>(3rd Feb 2019)</em>.</p>

<p><em><strong>Role in  Project:</strong> Designed the circuits and their PCBs, planning the overall method</em></p>

